				<li style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt; line-height:23pt; list-style-position:inside; margin:7.8pt 0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">用户在遵守本协议的前提下</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">，依法享有</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">东风金融-创格</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">平台提供的服务</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">。</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">东风金融-创格供应链平台为</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">开单人</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">、</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">持</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">单人</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">（核心企业/供应商）</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">、</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">资金方</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">、担保人</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">提供不同的服务，以适应各自企业</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">角色</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">的业务场景。</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">开单人</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">为</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">开新平台</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">内根据记账凭证记载具有款项支付义务的企业</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">，</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">以</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">资产（</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">东风金融-创格</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">或记账凭证）</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">登记</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">及付款</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">为主要功能</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">；</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">核心企业承担流转资产</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">（</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">东风金融-创格</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">或记账凭证）</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">的职责</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">，</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">且是融资的</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">可能</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">需求方，</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">承担</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">保证</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">企业信息及</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">资产</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">真实</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">可信</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">之责任</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">；供应商承担流转资产</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">（</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">东风金融-创格</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">或记账凭证）</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">的职责，并且是融资的</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">可能</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">需求方，平台支持其进行资产流转</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">及</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">融资</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">申请</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">；</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">资金方具备</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">受让东风金融-创格所载的应收账款债权，并向核心企业</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">、</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">供应商支付对价</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">的能力；担保方对机构受让方承担差额补足的担保责任，当经销商到期未向资金方足额偿还时，担保方向资金方补足该差额款项</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt">。</span></li>
